tcpdump -qtnni eth0

#############

tcpdump

-w write to file
-c number of packets

-q quiet
-t dont print timestamp
-nn dont resolv addresses or ports

-A ascii
-X hex and ascii

-I monitor mode

-Q direction in out inout

-vvv

-Z drop privs user

#############

icmp,arp,ip,ip6,tcp,udp

